Create main class object

{% raw %} 
sdk = ProductSdk(branch = 'dev-manual', user=USER, pw=PW)
{% endraw %}

Upload lots of data using s3

{% raw %} 
%%time
result = sdk.updateWithS3(
    sampleProducts,
    invocationType = 'RequestResponse'
  )
result
